{
  "stem": "2916.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then in the evening, Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Kardosz his name, a neighbor whose son was also studying in Budapest, ran over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had heard the terrible rumors about Jews being arrested, that the Germans had occupied Budapest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he was in a panic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he asked my father, have you heard anything from Bubbe?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father admitted that Bubbe was home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we heard about the occupation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father sent him back, because my parents didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Kardosz said, I'm leaving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm going tomorrow morning to bring my son home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he ran away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he left the next morning for Budapest, and he never returned.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Neither he nor his son ever returned.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we knew [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that we were in serious trouble.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And during the night of the next day, my brother arrived again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He managed to come home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that day, I will never forget my parents, the tension.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've never seen my mother break down and cry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She's a-- was a very stoic, very strong woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a horrible, horrible day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then late at night, again, my brother arrived just like the two days before during the night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The reason he managed to get home without being detected is that he was tall and blond and didn't look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he just evaded the military police, which both the Germans and the Hungarian military stepped up their-- their vigilance.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they would then participate in taking Jews off the trains, from the streets, from street cars, from everywhere.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It wasn't yet the systematic deportation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But there was this on-site arrests.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And these people who were arrested were put on-- on trains and were taken away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So, the next--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
